+description: Use this skill when editing the agent-vitals single-file dashboard, dashboard HTTP API, docs site, README metric explanations, source selectors, date filters, chart data, or user-facing dashboard documentation. Keywords: dashboard.html, serveDashboard, React CDN, Recharts, /api/metrics, docs/index.html.
